				\begin{document}$$ r^{\prime 2} , $$\end{document}</tex-math><inline-graphic xlink:href="439_2011_1118_Article_IEq14.gif"/></alternatives></inline-formula> in Microsoft Excel 2007. We found that under the null hypothesis <italic>p</italic>-value correlation coefficient,<inline-formula id="IEq15"><alternatives><tex-math id="M15">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
